race.description: Winkle Draper & O.t. Murray Memorial Maiden Plate
race.comment: BEDDA MIA (8) starting to hit her straps and set to peak at her fifth run back. Warmed up late when second over 1000m at Gundagai. Gets every chance today. TRAVELON DORY (12) appreciated the claim when she sat on the pace at her second race start to secure third over 1000m at Gundagai. Has more to offer and not to be overlooked. RUSKY RIPPER (4) struggled to run the 1100m out at Gilgandra. Goes into the exotics over this trip. XTRASCENT (6) is on debut for the Gratz Vella stable - who are in form of late. Looked a good thing at Moruya before their meeting was postponed on Friday. Draw is sticky, but he showed good speed in his trial and a forward showing is anticipated.
